</div>
</li>
<li>
<div class="icon-container">
<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="1" y="5" width="15" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><path d="m17 10 5-5v14l-5-5"></path></svg>
