<p>To reinforce learning and aid with revision, we offer the option to record each session. This is accompanied by AI-generated notes with timestamps, which allows students to quickly access key moments and revisit topics at their convenience.</p>
</div>
</li>
</ul>

<div class="cta-section">
<h2>Still Need Help?</h2>
<p>Our expert tutors are ready to provide the one-to-one support your child needs. Book a free consultation to get started today!</p>
<a href="/consultations" class="cta-button">
Book Your Free Consultation and Taster Session
</a>
</div>
</main>
<Footer />
</body>
</html>
<style>
:root {
--primary-color: var(--accent);
--text-color: var(--accent);
--card-bg-color: #f9f9f9;
--box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
}

body {
    font-family: sans-serif;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
}

main {
    color: var(--accent);
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 2em auto;
    padding: 0 1em;
    box-sizing: border-box;
}

h1 {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-size: clamp(1.8em, 5vw, 2.5em);
    text-align: center;
}

h2 {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-size: clamp(1.5em, 4vw, 1.8em);
    margin-top: 2em;
}

p {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-size: clamp(1em, 2vw, 1.1em);
}

    /* Final CTA Section */
    .cta-section {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 4em;
        padding: 2.5em;
        background-color: white;
        border-radius: 12px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        color: var(--accent);
    }
    
    .cta-section h2 {
        font-size: clamp(1.5em, 4vw, 1.8em);
        margin-top: 0;
        color: var(--accent);
    }
    .cta-section p {
        margin-bottom: 1.5em;
    }

    .cta-button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 1em 2em;
        background-color: var(--accent-pop);
        color: white;
        font-weight: bold;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    }

    .cta-button:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
        box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }

ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
}

li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1.5em;
    margin-bottom: 1.5em;
    line-height: 1.5;
    background-color: var(--card-bg-color);
    padding: 1.5em;
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
    word-break: break-word;
}

.icon-container {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    color: var(--accent);
}

.icon-container svg {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
}

.text-container strong {
    display: block;
    font-size: clamp(1.1em, 2.5vw, 1.2em);
    margin-bottom: 0.5em;
}

.text-container p {
    margin: 0;
}

@media (max-width: 600px) {
    li {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        text-align: center;
    }
}
</style>